name: Algorithmlib
tagline: A library for math and algorithms.
body:
AlgorithmLib is a library with mathematical objects and algorithms. 

Here are the classes we have so far:
* [AlgLib::Polynomial](https://github.com/fclvbfm934/AlgorithmLib/wiki/AlgLib::Polynomial)   
   - [AlgLib::IntegerPolynomial](https://github.com/fclvbfm934/AlgorithmLib/wiki/AlgLib::IntegerPolynomial)
* [AlgLib::Fraction](https://github.com/fclvbfm934/AlgorithmLib/wiki/AlgLib::Fraction)
* [AlgLib::Permutation](https://github.com/fclvbfm934/AlgorithmLib/wiki/AlgLib::Permutation)
